text: Quantez is a 1957 American action western movie directed by Harry Keller and starring Fred MacMurray, Dorothy Malone, Sydney Chaplin, John Gavin, John Larch, Michael Ansara. It was distributed by Universal Pictures. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1957 action movies Category:1950s Western (genre) movies Category:American action movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:Movies directed by Harry Keller Category:Universal Pictures movies
